  "description": {
    "en": {
      "provenance": "imported",
      "value": "Construction Work 1. Build 1 school building with 12 rooms in Sankhuwasabha district.2.  Build 1 school building with 18 rooms in Rolpa district.3. Build Separate Toilets For Ladise and gents with Sewage Treatment system in Rolpa district.4. Provide electrical work and building painting support.5. Manage water supply system in the schools with the source used in the community.6. Provide school furniture, Outdoor playing materials, school uniform and stationary.7. Provide Teacher allowance support to Pangboche P.S., Gautam Buddha P.S. and Sundi L.S. School.8. Feasibility Study work for new projects."
    },
